**StreamSyncScope**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes real-time metrics across synchronized data sources with smooth scrolling and peak indicators.

```markdown
# StreamSyncScope - Multi-Source Metric Viewer

StreamSyncScope displays incoming data from parallel sources and highlights sync delays, jumps, or divergence.

## Features
- Synchronized stream plotting  
- Live scrollable view  
- Matplotlib backend

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamSyncScope.git
cd StreamSyncScope
python visualize.py
